   "source": [
    "# Order\n",
    "\n",
    "An order $<$ on a set $S$ is a relation that satisfies the following properties:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. For all $x, y \\in S$: either $x < y$, or $y < x$, or $x = y$.\n",
    "2. For all $x, y, z \\in S$: if $x < y$ and $y < z$, then $x < z$."
   ]
  }
 ],
